original_title: TNA One Night Only: Joker's Wild 4
overview: Twenty-four men and two women compete in a tournament for $100,000. It consisted of tag team matches in which the partners were randomly drawn in a lottery and teams had to work together to advance to the main event Battle Royal, with the grand prize of US$100,000. Some of the matches took place on January 7 and 9, 2016, from the Sands Bethlehem Event Center in Bethlehem, Pennsylvania while the other took place on January 30â€“31, 2016, from the Wembley Arena at London, England and the Barclaycard Arena at Birmingham, England, and aired on PPV on March 4, 2016.
title: TNA One Night Only: Joker's Wild 4
